data.title: badge, German, 75 Massen Kundgebungen in Leipzig 1937, DAF
data.meta_description: Circular, die-cast, metal badge in a silver finish. On the face is a central design depicting an emblem of an eagle with outstretched wings, clasping a circular wreath containing a swastika, with the date inscription 1937 either side. Above the eagle is a section of the DAF logo of a swastika within a cogged wheel, with an adjacent factory scene.
